_json.description: Easy DIY Recycled Card Garland. Looking for recycled card craft ideas? Try turning old greeting cards into colorful garland for spring. Create FREE spring home decor and add some cheer to your mantles and windows. It's a great craft idea to keep kids entertained too! Reuse greeting cards to make DIY garland for spring and save money on home decor - and save those pretty greeting cards from the recycling pile. This upcycled paper garland will definitely put a smile on your face. #recycledcards
